OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FAs of Friday night, Blue Islands has
OL,7,Fcancelled all of its future flights
OL,8,Fand suspended its operations.
OL,10,FAny tickets for future Blue Islands
OL,11,Fflights will no longer be valid, and
OL,12,Fany passengers hoping to travel
OL,13,Fonwards will need to book with other
OL,14,Fairlines.
OL,16,FThis has caused huge disruption and
OL,17,Fdistress for many travellers who had
OL,18,Fplans to travel in the immediate
OL,19,Ffuture and over the Christmas period.
