OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FBecause Blue Islands is a company that
OL,7,Fwas established in Alderney, UK travel
OL,8,Fprotections do not apply.
OL,10,FThe governments of Jersey and Guernsey
OL,11,Fare not expected to fund repatriation
OL,12,Fflights for any travellers left
OL,13,Fstranded by Blue Island's suspension
OL,14,Fof operations.
OL,16,FAny replacement flights you choose
OL,17,Fwill have to be booked at your own
OL,18,Fexpense.
