OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FBlue Islands has told customers with
OL,7,Fbookings made directly to them to
OL,8,F"contact your bank or provider of the
OL,9,Fpayment card used to make the booking.
OL,11,F"For bookings made through a travel
OL,12,Fagent or holiday company, please
OL,13,Fcontact the company through whom you
OL,14,Fbooked for advice and guidance."
OL,16,FIf you purchased travel insurance that
OL,17,Fincludes cover for scheduled airline
OL,18,Ffailure (SAFI), you should contact
OL,19,Fyour insurer to enquire about next
OL,20,Fsteps.
