OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FThe UK Civil Aviation Authority has
OL,7,Fadvised: "Some airlines and airline
OL,8,Fticket agents will offer customers
OL,9,Feither a specific (SAFI) policy or
OL,10,Finclude similar protection within a
OL,11,Fbroader travel insurance product.
OL,13,F"The type of protection provided may
OL,14,Fvary depending on the type of policy
OL,15,Ftaken out.
OL,17,F"A policy may simply cover the cost of
OL,18,Fthe original tickets purchased or any
OL,19,Funused portion, or the additional cost
OL,20,Fof purchasing new flights."
