OL,6,FWill I have protection from my credit
OL,7,For debit card provider?
OL,9,FIf you booked your flights using a
OL,10,Fcredit card, then you may be protected
OL,11,Funder Section 75 of the UK Consumer
OL,12,FCredit Act 1974, which is included in
OL,13,Fthe terms and conditions of most
OL,14,Fcredit card accounts.
