OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FUnder this Section, if you paid more
OL,7,Fthan #100 for goods and services which
OL,8,Fwere not delivered, or the firm
OL,9,Fproviding them went bust, your credit
OL,10,Fcard provider will be jointly liable
OL,11,Fwith your supplier, and should
OL,12,Ftherefore provide a full refund.
OL,14,FIf you booked using a Visa or
OL,15,FMastercard debit card, then you may be
OL,16,Feligible for a protection scheme known
OL,17,Fas 'chargeback'.
