OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FChargeback allows customers to cancel
OL,7,Ftransactions if problems occur, and is
OL,8,Fnot limited to purchases of #100 or
OL,9,Fmore, but does have time limits of as
OL,10,Flittle as 120 days to apply.
OL,12,FTo claim this back, you will need a
OL,13,FNegative Response Letter from aviation
OL,14,Fauthorities to confirm that Blue
OL,15,FIslands has ceased operating.
OL,17,FAt present, the company has not yet
OL,18,Fbeen declared insolvent, and thus no
OL,19,Fsuch document is available.
