OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FITV News understands that it will not
OL,7,Fbe known until next week if and when
OL,8,Fthe company will lodge for insolvency.
OL,10,FHowever, the Jersey Consumer Council
OL,11,Fhas promised to post the relevant
OL,12,Fdocumentation on its website when it
OL,13,Fbecomes available - which will be
OL,14,Fvalid for people across the Channel
OL,15,FIslands seeking refunds from their
OL,16,Frespective banks.
OL,18,FUntil this date, however, islanders
OL,19,Fwho paid by debit card will not be
OL,20,Fable to claim a refund.
