OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FWill the collapse of Blue Islands
OL,7,Fimpact medical patients?
OL,9,FPatients who travel from Jersey to
OL,10,FSouthampton for treatment may be
OL,11,Fconcerned about how the collapse of
OL,12,FBlue Islands, formerly the only
OL,13,Fairline offering direct links to the
OL,14,Fcity, could impact them.
OL,16,FIslanders travel to Southampton
OL,17,FGeneral Hospital for a range of
OL,18,Ftreatments, including outpatient
OL,19,Fappointments, surgeries, radiotherapy
OL,20,Fand extensive procedures.
