OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,FClaire Thompson, Chief Operating
OL,7,FOfficer of Acute Services at Jersey
OL,8,FHospital, told ITV News: "A support
OL,9,Fteam has been put in place to reassure
OL,10,Fall patients that we will be working
OL,11,Fwith them to reschedule all of their
OL,12,Fflights, and we've got additional team
OL,13,Fmembers in place.
OL,15,F"We are contacting all patients who
OL,16,Fwill be initially affected over the
OL,17,Fweekend".
OL,19,FShe continues that they are
OL,20,Fprioritising patients in terms of
OL,21,Ftheir medical needs and conditions.
