OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,F"We're very focused on the clinical
OL,7,Fpriority and making sure those
OL,8,Fpatients that need to get off the
OL,9,Fisland for treatment - whether that's
OL,10,Fsurgery or cancer treatment, we're
OL,11,Ffocusing on those first".
OL,13,FShe added that more resources have
OL,14,Fbeen allocated to their overseas
OL,15,Ftravel office, which is contacting
OL,16,Fpatients who were due to depart the
OL,17,Fisland imminently for treatment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@XO]
