OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,F"We're also working with other flight
OL,7,Foperators to ensure we can reschedule
OL,8,Fthose bookings for flights, and using
OL,9,Fferries where possible".
OL,11,FLoganair is stepping in from Sunday to
OL,12,Freplace air links between the Channel
OL,13,FIslands and Southampton, which Claire
OL,14,Fsays will hopefully ease patients'
OL,15,Fconcerns about potentially missing
OL,16,Ftreatments and appointments.
OL,18,FShe continues that so far, "no
OL,19,Fpatients have been affected".
