OL,3,CMy Blue Islands flight has been
OL,4,Ccancelled. What now?
OL,6,F"I appreciate this is worrying for
OL,7,Fpatients and I want to reassure them
OL,8,Fwe're confident the measures we've put
OL,9,Fin place mean there will be no impact
OL,10,Fon patients awaiting treatment off-
OL,11,Fisland," she adds.
OL,13,FIslanders are encouraged to keep an
OL,14,Feye on the government website for more
OL,15,Finformation as the situation unfolds.
OL,17,FCircumstances are slightly different
OL,18,Fin Guernsey since Blue Islands wasn't
OL,19,Fthe only provider of direct flights to
OL,20,FSouthampton, with Aurigny also
OL,21,Foffering this connection.
