OL,7,Fconcerned about the fate of existing
OL,8,Fflights booked with Blue Islands.
OL,10,FBella Farrell, CEO of Health
OL,11,FConnections in Guernsey, told ITV
OL,12,FNews: "We are making sure patients
OL,13,Fhave up-to-date information and anyone
OL,14,Fwho is concerned should contact Health
OL,15,Fand Social Care".
